Using a macro in IE7 in simple situations produces forced newlines and regular newlines when saving from the RTE.

Eg
{noformat}
{cheese}
{noformat}

round-trips through IE7 to
{noformat}
{cheese}\\
{noformat}

and

{noformat}
blah
{cheese}
{noformat}

round-trips to 

{noformat}
blah

{cheese}\\
{noformat}

which round-trips to


{noformat}
blah


{cheese}\\
{noformat}


This is not the case in 2.10.0

